===Noun===
'''felony'''
#a [[severe]] [[crime]], usually punishable upon [[conviction]] by a large [[fine]] or by a term of [[imprisonment]] longer than one year or by a combination of fine and imprisonment. Crimes which are punishable by small fines and/or by imprisonment for less than one year are usually called [[misdemeanor]]s.
